-- agent-demo.fl — Autonomous Agent Demo
-- Demonstrates the Run agent with goal construct.
-- The agent reasons, picks tools, and completes the goal step by step.
-- Run: fluent run examples/agent-demo.fl
-- No API key = mock mode (agent runs with simulated responses)

Output "═══════════════════════════════════════════════".
Output "  Autonomous Agent Demo".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════════════".
Output "".

-- ── Agent 1: File analysis task ──────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── Agent 1: File Task ──".

@agent(model: claude, max_steps: 8)
@tools(read_file, write_file, run_calculation)
Run agent with goal "Read the file examples/assets/sample.txt, count its words, then write a one-sentence summary to examples/assets/agent_output.txt" and call the outcome file_task.

Output "".
If file_task.success is true, then output "Agent completed the file task.".
Otherwise, output "Agent stopped early.".
Output file_task.steps_taken.

Output "".

-- ── Agent 2: Calculation chain ──────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── Agent 2: Math Task ──".

@agent(model: claude, max_steps: 5)
@tools(run_calculation, remember, recall)
Run agent with goal "Calculate the compound interest on $10,000 at 5% annual rate for 3 years, then remember the result" and call the outcome math_task.

Output "".
If math_task.success is true, then output "Math agent answer:".
If math_task.success is true, then output math_task.answer.

Output "".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════════════".
Output "  Agent demo complete.".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════════════".
